# Force LF everywhere, regardless of the cloning machine's OS or git
# core.autocrlf setting. Without this, a Windows checkout with the common
# core.autocrlf=true default silently rewrites every text file to CRLF -
# including the bash embedded in docker-compose.yml's `command:` blocks and
# the Makefile, both of which break when read by a Linux container/make.
* text=auto eol=lf

*.png binary
*.jpg binary
*.jpeg binary
*.parquet binary
